			<h3 class="first"><a href="#p22543">Charming Aggro</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=22543#p22543"><img src="./styles/prosilver/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><span style="color: #FF6666;" class="username-coloured">Adreanne</span></strong> &raquo; Feb 3rd, '04, 01:17 </p>

			

			<div class="content">Could any one explain the exact mechanics of charm aggro and how it works? I.E. if there is a limit to when an NPC won't tank, and will tank, multiple charmed pets, summoned pets etc.... Want to know even the most minut details.</div>

			

		</div>

		
			<dl class="postprofile" id="profile22543">
