			<div class="content">Raynboh has it right.  I will often farm for tinkering components in Plane of Innovation with a DC pet.  Sometimes a ranger will work on archery.  Still OK.  Then a bard drops in with an area song.  Still OK.  Then, someone will <span style="font-style: italic">help</span> by dotting the mob or something, and I am now tanking.  Fortunately, once slowed, they are fairly easy to tank, but it takes mana.
<br />
<br />As an aside, has anyone come up with a strategy to use the DC pet against Archaic Units (unslowable)?</div>

