<br />
<br />4 aggro rule is for random charmed pets only, it does not apply for any to summoned, dc or temp pets. rule is you+your pet (you get aggro because it's your charmed pet dosn't matter how far you are form fight) plus two others can be on aggro list of the mob, otherwise that mob ignores your charmed pets aggro and goes to the next highest. the two other targets may be a person+pet or two other people. I don't think a wizard fimilair counts as part of the 4 but i can't varify that. this rule does not stop a normal summoned pet or even a dc pet from keeping aggro.
<br />
