			<div class="content">The 4-agro rule isn't mythical. It was stated in plain English in the patch message along with the new experience rules.  I don't know how to get it, but it's been reposted here a couple times in charm-xp threads, so I'm sure somebody can.  It was part of the "charm nerf".  There were three changes: experience, resist modifier on CoD, and pet tanking.
<br />
<br />Of course, we have to remind people about that patch pretty regularly, since people *still* think the 2-year-old developer post on charm xp applies, when these changes are much more recent.  Perhaps a copy of that patch message should be stickyed somewhere.</div>

			

