<br />
<br />1.  Pull mob, set pet on it.
<br />2.  Slow mob
<br />3.  Heal pet
<br />4.  Tash mob
<br />5.  Sit back and watch the fun.
<br />
<br />Never a problem when there is a single group at zone in.  Tthe other group pulls and starts to fight next to my mob.  At that time, the mob is off my pet and onto me.  It doesn't matter how long the fight has been going on, I get agro.</div>

